'''Brooks Propulsion Devices''' ('''BPD''') was a company that specialized in propulsion systems for [[Astromech droid/Legends|astromech droids]], notably anti-grav booster components for [[Industrial Automaton/Legends|Industrial Automaton]] [[R-series/Legends|R-series]] [[Droid/Legends|droids]].

Brooks Propulsion Devices was shut down by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] following the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

